It’s a jungle out there: Shift4 Payments CEO on the future of restaurant tech
Technology editor Nancy Luna offers news and insights from the floor of FSTEC.
Megan McCutcheon | Aug 13, 2018

Editor's Note: This is one in a series of dispatches from Nation's
Restaurant News and Restaurant Hospitality
covering the FSTEC technology show, held
Sept.30-Oct. 2 in Orlando, Fla.

When it comes to descriptors for today's
restaurant technology landscape, Jared Isaacman
doesn't mince words.

"It's a jungle," Isaacman, founder and CEO of
Shift4 Payments, said at the FSTEC conference
in Orlando, Fla. on Monday,
